=head1 DESCRIPTION

Specifies how retrieved results from a knowledge base are reranked to
improve relevance.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 BedrockRerankingConfiguration => L<Paws::BedrockAgent::VectorSearchBedrockRerankingConfiguration>

Specifies the configuration for using an Amazon Bedrock reranker model
to rerank retrieved results.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Type => Str

Specifies the type of reranking model to use. Currently, the only
supported value is C<BEDROCK_RERANKING_MODEL>.



